  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to assess the implicitement of the cholesterol 24 S hydroxylase gene
      and the 24 S hydroxycholesterol in glaucoma and in age related macular degeneration.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
